The paper deals with clustering and labelling journal articles, which are typically related to information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), deep learning (cs.DL), and databases (cs.DB). The proposed method of using mutual information to label clusters is a common technique in these sub-categories.
